data.description: Sellers are willing to help buy down interest rate or help with closing costs with an acceptable offer! This 3 bed, 2 bath home sits on two spacious lots for almost half an acre of land! Tucked away at the end of a cul de sac, with tons of beautiful mature oak trees in a quiet neighborhood. You are only a few blocks away from the Ivy Lane nature site for afternoon strolls to enjoy nature and birding. The large open floor plan is light and airy and there is no carpet in the whole house! The kitchen has ample counter space, a huge pantry and new stainless steel stove and dishwasher. The large master suite boasts an extra large walk-in closet and ensuite full bathroom. Across the house you will find two guest rooms and a full bathroom. The large open living room is perfect for entertaining. As you open the backdoors you are greeted by oak trees in your extra large back yard. There is a bonus side yard that isn't fenced that would be perfect for boat or RV storage.Plus a two car garage!
